{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be minimalist and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Smart Home Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #3498db;\n            --secondary-blue: #5dade2;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --card-background: #2a2a2a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-blue), var(--secondary-blue));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-card {\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-card h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            padding: 80px 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            color: #ccc;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        /* Basic Font Awesome integration (for icons) */\n        .fa {\n            display: inline-block;\n            font: normal normal normal 14px/1 FontAwesome;\n            font-size: inherit;\n            text-rendering: auto;\n            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\n        }\n        .fa-solid { font-weight: 900; }\n        .fa-light { font-weight: 300; }\n        .fa-regular { font-weight: 400; }\n        .fa-brands { font-weight: 400; }\n\n        /* Example Icons (replace with actual Font Awesome CDN if you have it) */\n        .icon-placeholder {\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 60px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Smart Home Solutions</h1>\n            <p>Experience the Future of Living</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Innovative Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-placeholder\"><i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i></div>\n                    <h3>Smart Lighting</h3>\n                    <p>Automate your lights, adjust brightness, and set moods with intuitive controls.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-placeholder\"><i class=\"fas fa-thermometer-half\"></i></div>\n                    <h3>Climate Control</h3>\n                    <p>Maintain the perfect temperature effortlessly, saving energy and enhancing comfort.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-placeholder\"><i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i></div>\n                    <h3>Home Security</h3>\n                    <p>Monitor your home from anywhere with smart locks, cameras, and alert systems.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-placeholder\"><i class=\"fas fa-music\"></i></div>\n                    <h3>Entertainment Systems</h3>\n                    <p>Seamlessly integrate your audio and visual devices for an immersive experience.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\n            <p style=\"max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.1em;\">\n                We are dedicated to making your home smarter, safer, and more energy-efficient. Our cutting-edge technology is designed to be user-friendly, seamlessly integrating into your daily life. Experience unparalleled convenience and peace of mind with our smart home solutions.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Smart Home Solutions. All rights reserved. | Privacy Policy | Terms of Service</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}